Title: The Carl Household
Body: The Year's Events - 1994 I'll briefly recap the year's events:  I began Graduate School in January, then there was an eclipse in May which I saw for about 5 seconds during a break in the clouds, then a comet struck Jupiter over a period of days during the summer (a nice picture of this event is here ), then Rice beat Texas in football for the first time since I was two (resulting in nature wreaking havoc as heavy rains inundated Houston), then the Republicans became the majority party in the House of Representatives, then I finished my first year of Graduate School.
